TY  - JOUR
T1  - Generation Gap? The Branching Influence of Historical Myths
AU  - Noh, Sung-Chul
AU  - Lyle, Matthew C. B.
AU  - Do, Boram
Y1  - 2025/02/12
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/09/01
